open chrome
	choose in tools development tools, then 

	指定源码里的不同地方，可以看到参数，比如h1标题，这个用可以看到具体的字体大小，
	图片，可以看到具体的border，width等

	browser use dom(document object model)to interpret html tags,
		so source code you see are just interpreted code by browser, not source code

css decide how every element in html will look(like color, border...)
html decide struct and content of whole page

查看页面图片源码，右键检查,所有图片都是方形的,
	html决定位置，或者上传图片，在线直接的图形可以用
	css直接得到，再另外一边的样式里可以调大小和颜色
		还可以勾选与否一些特性，可以改变形状

	分析图形的时候应该使用方形来切割图片

<head>
	<link rel="sytlesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
</head>
<div class="xxx">content</div>

CSS: 层叠风格表单，就是多个重叠的风格描述
then in .css file, use 
p {} used to applied to all paragraph
.xxx {
	color:red
}  then this css style is applied onto your html file 
可以在页面的另一个源码框内elemnt style中现场更改style

display:flex 这个可以把属性合并到一行里面
通过方框的 margin 来调整边距

<p> <h1> ...  这些是块级元素。浏览器会在前后加空格，在上下加空行

<!--This is a comment-->
all blank line will be cancelled when parse(only one will be reserved for splitting word)

label
	<br /> (create a bland line) some label should close in the open tab like this
	<head>   <title>  this should be put in head to set a head of title, meta data
		<meta charset="utf-8"> is important to recognize other language!!
	<a href=xxxx>xxx </a>  a hyper link
	<img src=xxx width=  height=  alt=   />   add an image, alt will be output if img can not find
	<hr /> a horizon line
	<pre>  resserve the structure what you type
	<bdo dir="rtl"> xxxx</bdo>   used to reverse direction of word

attr:
	generally can be applied:
		class, id, style, title
	align="center" (used in h1 h2 ...)
	bgcolor="yellow" (used in <body>
	border="1"   table's border used in <table> or <img />
	style="backgroud-color:red   can be put in <h1 h2  ....







